parameters.name: EndTime
parameters.description: The end of the time range to query. The value is a UNIX timestamp that is accurate to seconds.

parameters.name: Lang
parameters.description:
The language of the content within the request and the response. Valid values:

*   **zh** (default): Chinese
*   **en**: English

parameters.name: StartTime
parameters.description: The beginning of the time range to query. The value is a UNIX timestamp that is accurate to seconds.
